{"tha-ap268:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap268:0.2":"Padumukkhipavagga ","tha-ap268:0.3":"Macchadayakattheraapadana ","tha-ap268:1.1":"“Candabhaganaditire, ","tha-ap268:1.2":"ukkuso asaham tada; ","tha-ap268:1.3":"Mahantam maccham paggayha, ","tha-ap268:1.4":"siddhatthamunino adam. ","tha-ap268:2.1":"Catunnavutito kappe, ","tha-ap268:2.2":"yam macchamadadim tada; ","tha-ap268:2.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap268:2.4":"macchadanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap268:3.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap268:3.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap268:3.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap268:4.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma macchadayako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap268:5.1":"Macchadayakattherassapadanam chattham. "}